#

Classic Guacamole

10 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

snackdiphealthy

Description

A creamy avocado dip with a zesty lime twist, perfect for snacking or as a topping.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • diced tomatoes: 1/2 cup
  • minced red onion: 1/4 cup
  • chopped cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: a pinch
